<div id="home">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-12">
        <h1>{{msg}}</h1>
        <h2>Welcome to SharkNo!</h2>
        <p>We don't have anything against sharks, per se. They have their place in the food chain. We just don't want to be below them in that chain. Probably you don't either. Use our site to find out about shark sightings and attacks at the beach where you're going. Or, report what you've seen to warn others. To start, choose Search or Report. </p>
        <form class="clearfix mb-4" action="POST">
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="example-text">Example Text</label>
            <input type="text" id="example-text" class="form-control" aria-describedby="example-text"
              placeholder="Enter Example Text">
          </div>
          <div class="form-group">
            <label for="example-description">Example Description</label>
            <textarea class="form-control" id="example-description" aria-describedby="example-description"
              placeholder="Enter Example Description"></textarea>
          </div>
          <button id="submit" class="btn btn-primary float-right">Submit</button>          <button id="search" class="btn btn-primary float-right">Search</button>
        </form>
        </div>
        <h3>Examples:</h3>
        <ul id="example-list" class="list-group">
          {{#each examples}}
          <li data-id="{{this.id}}" class="list-group-item">
            <a href="example/{{this.id}}">{{this.Year}}: {{this.Country}}, {{this.Area}}, {{this.Location}}</a>
            <button class="btn btn-danger float-right delete">ï½˜</button>
          </li>
          {{/each}}
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="container">
  <h3 class="mb-4"> Enter What You Saw</h3>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-3">
      <form class="clearfix mb-4" action="POST">
        <div class="form-group">
          <label for="date">Date of Occurrence DD/MM/YY</label>
          <input type="text" id="date" class="form-control" aria-describedby="date" placeholder="Enter date">
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-3">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="country">Country </label>
        <input type="text" id="country" class="form-control" aria-describedby="country" placeholder="Enter Country">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-3">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="area">Area (State, etc.) </label>
        <input type="text" id="area" class="form-control" aria-describedby="area" placeholder="Enter Area">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-3">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="location">Location (City)</label>
        <input type="text" id="location" class="form-control" aria-describedby="location" placeholder="Enter location">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-4">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="activity">Activity (Standing, Surfing etc...) </label>
        <input type="text" id="activity" class="form-control" aria-describedby="activity" placeholder="Enter activity">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-4">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="species">Species (White shark, Tiger shark etc..) </label>
        <input type="text" id="species" class="form-control" aria-describedby="species" placeholder="Enter species">
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="col-4">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="type">Type (Unprovoked, Provoked, Invalid etc..) </label>
        <input type="text" id="type" class="form-control" aria-describedby="type" placeholder="Enter Type">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-9">
      <div class="form-group">
        <label for="injury">Injury - describe what happend </label>
        <input style="height: 250px;" type="text" id="injury" class="form-control" aria-describedby="injury"
          placeholder="Text">
      </div>
      <button id="submit1" class="btn btn-primary float-left">Submit1</button>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
